{"tid":421403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗議警方鎮壓 撐加泰獨立團體號召明大罷工","createTime":"2017-10-02T08:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T02:20:36.000Z","uid":51904,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea750e18a76790863505ec10353b5155b388f2b","tid":421403,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:21:47.000Z","msg":"西班牙加泰羅尼亞自治區公投結束後，西班牙兩大工會號召在加泰羅尼亞舉行大罷工，抗議警方對加泰選民使用暴力。<br />\n<br />\nUGT和CCOO兩個工會、獨派團體「加泰羅尼亞國民會議」（ANC），以及41個團體發表聲明，指西班牙警方嚴重侵權利與自由，號召大罷工。<br />\n<br />\n另外，加泰羅尼亞撐獨組織Omnium的負責人奎薩特（Jordi Cuixart）亦號召支持獨立的團體和工會周二在加泰羅尼亞大罷工。<br />\n<br />\n加泰羅尼亞的經濟產量約相當於西班牙國內生產總的1/5，加泰羅尼亞的經濟規模和智利相當。"},{"pid":"98b37d02290fb9093d6c5d95645975e73ef0bfb9","tid":421403,"uid":51904,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"港獨會唔會號召到大罷工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a801d4cbaf3a20408df7ea4e1fb135bfb3d02ece","tid":421403,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港獨會唔會號召到大罷工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇到好難喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b60d49d6a4586b841dea2650866132bfeb656e","tid":421403,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:35:44.000Z","msg":"等睇西班牙中央統媒：加泰罷工係經濟暴力，爲違憲獨立而挾持全西班牙經濟<br />\n乜乜乜"},{"pid":"5fa01e402d7716b0017faccb8a390fd898d01f38","tid":421403,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9ca6e9b782467a7cbeb803085c0d0f286cacb8","tid":421403,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:37:50.000Z","msg":"點解人地非暴力抗爭都可以吊打港豬"},{"pid":"7f1cff3c9cc25e612577872ad070fdeeb8cba73b","tid":421403,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"repl